(1,'1711841760155351','By partnering with a third-party on-demand delivery provider','You can join a partner program of an existing on-demand delivery\r\napp to offer the delivery of your product using their user base and\r\nplatform. Thus, you will be able to cut the costs of setting up your\r\nown delivery program','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632543787about1.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632543787about3.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632543787about.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/thu_1632543787about_50_50.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632543787about2.png',1,'2021-09-25 09:53:07'),
(2,'1711846312723964','By building a dedicated app for your business purposes','If you\r\nown a flower shop or a pharmacy, you can offer on-demand\r\ndeliveries to your customers using this app. One of the most\r\nsuccessful and widely known examples of this is AnyWare service by\r\nDominoâ€™s Pizza. https://anyware.dominos.com/\r\nRegardless of the chosen approach, offering a fast and convenient\r\ndelivery service is a powerful competitive benefit that can set you\r\napart from your competition in a certain niche. The following\r\nexamples of successful on-demand delivery apps further prove this\r\npoint.\r\nThis means peer to peer delivery services, where you request a\r\ncourier to pick up your stuff at one location and bring it to another\r\none. This approach is popular with services like parcel delivery,\r\nlaundry (e.g. Rinse), etc. Moreover, it can be blended with personalshopper assistant services, where you ask a person to go to the store,\r\nbuy something for you and deliver it to your home (e.g. Quiqup).\r\nhttps://www.rinse.com/ https://www.quiqup.com/ ,\r\nhttps://easternpeak.com/bl','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632543966banner1.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632543966banner3.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632543966banner.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/thu_1632543966banner_50_50.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632543966banner2.png',1,'2021-09-25 09:56:06'),
(3,'1711846426457904','Goods delivery','This approach can be applied to practically any product, from flowers\r\n(BloomThat), gifts, to medications (NowRX), groceries (Instacart) or\r\neven marijuana (Canary). These on-demand local delivery apps\r\nattract users because of their wide range of products available,\r\nscheduling for preferred delivery time slots, and doorstep service','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632544104entertainments1.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632544104entertainments3.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632544104entertainments.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/thu_1632544104entertainments_50_50.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632544104entertainments2.png',1,'2021-09-25 09:58:24'),
(4,'1711846586610348','Moving and furniture delivery','This includes on-demand truck and hauling services (Lugg or Dolly).\r\nYou just set your pickup location and destination, choose the size of\r\nvehicle that is right for you, and the preferred arrival time. Once the\r\norder is picked up, you can message helpers in-app, and track your\r\nitems along the way.','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632544206restaurants1.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632544206restaurants3.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632544206restaurants.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/thu_1632544206restaurants_50_50.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632544206restaurants2.png',1,'2021-09-25 10:00:06'),
(5,'1711846688509828','Food delivery','On-demand food delivery apps like Grubhub or UberEATS. The\r\nsegment is one of the most crowded These on-demand delivery\r\nservices deliver restaurant food and groceries with the help of their\r\nown delivery people, enabling us to have our favorite meal at our\r\ndoorsteps with a matter of a few clicks.\r\nPostmates, one of the first and most popular on-demand delivery\r\nservices has started as a courier/goods delivery business. Yet, the\r\ncompany recently pivoted to focus mostly on food delivery.','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632544353fi1.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632544353fi3.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632544353fi.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/thu_1632544353fi_50_50.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632544353fi2.png',1,'2021-09-25 10:02:33'),
(6,'1711853635449415','Peer to peer delivery marketplaces','These apps allow you to post a delivery request and get connected\r\nwith a person traveling in the desired direction (e.g. Nimber, Roadie,\r\nor Grabr). These marketplaces are less regulated and tend to focus on\r\ninternational deliveries, rather than local.\r\nRegardless of the specific model or segment these apps target, they\r\nshare common business logic and a number of key elements. So,\r\nhere are the must-have features of an on-demand delivery app','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632550911banner-21.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632550911banner-23.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632550911banner-2.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/thu_1632550911banner-2_50_50.png','uploads/delivery_category_images/1632550911banner-22.png',1,'2021-09-25 11:51:51'),
